Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:45.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,嬢ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,落ち着いてじっとしてたら　すぐ治まるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうして私が苦しくなったの　分かったの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:16.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,先家にいたら　窓の外で嬢ちゃんの声がしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,助けて　助けて　って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その方角にずっと行ったら　嬢ちゃんがいたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほんと？すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:31.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私　ずっと「スミ助けて」って思ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:35.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　また苦しくなったら呼んでよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:36.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　スミ　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっとうちにいてね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこにも遠くに行かないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:08.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さきほど　水路からチラリとお嬢さんをお見かけしたんですがね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:14.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お嬢さん　少々厄介な癖がお有りじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,癖？何のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,時折　抜け殻のようになって　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:28.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しばらく意識が戻らない　というような
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,放っておくと　ますます厄介なことになりますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:02.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,…ら　ゆら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっと戻ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何の用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この人がその癖を治してくれるそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲師のギンコと言います
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰も治してなんて言ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,出ていってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミと話してたもん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,またそれか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:38.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,バカなことを言ってないで　いい加減スミのことは忘れろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれはもううちの使用人をやめたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:49.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもスミは今でも　私が臥せってると分かってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「大丈夫」って言ってくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:57.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうしたら　苦しいのも楽になるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その人との間に　深い水脈が通ったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水脈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:15.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人と人の意識の間には　見えない通路があるという
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょうど　この町に張り巡らされた水路のように
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,裏庭ですべての水路は繋がっていて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:33.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこには「五識」を補うもの　我々の言う「妖質」というものが流れている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが水嵩が少ない所も多く　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おまけに入り組んでいて　地図もない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それでも水路は繋がっているので　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,望む相手に会えることもたまにある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:59.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すると　お互い同時に相手のことを思い出すようなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いわゆる「虫の知らせ」が起こるわけです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:08.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それを思うままに起こせる蟲がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,カイロギと言いましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妖質の豊かなものの意識に棲み
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:24.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,主と同調し　自由に水脈を往来し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,望む相手に思いを届けることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さんのようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私がスミのこと離れてても分かるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつも私のこと考えてくれてるからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲なんて関係ない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:51.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたが必要とすれば　誰の所にも行けるはずなんだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:56.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　繰り返しカイロギを使うと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,カイロギはやがて人の意識を乗せたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分の意思で動き始める
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:06.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すると人はその間　意識を奪われるようになる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:12.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そしていつかは　二度と意識は戻らなくなってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな　バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:22.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　当分その能力を使うのをやめさえすれば　害はない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,無理よ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:30.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,発作が起きたら　いつの間にかスミの所へ行ってしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,相当進行しちまっているようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妖質を一時的に枯らす薬がある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,飲めばカイロギは動けなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:48.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　発作が起きてスミの声が聞けなきゃ怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなもん　気のせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:57.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,胸の病は　じっとして気を落ち着かせていれば大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,急には難しいかも知れんが　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた一人の問題じゃねぇんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,って？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミさんの方からこっちへ来ることはあったか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:15.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　すでに伝染してるな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:23.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,同じ所へ繰り返し行けば　相手にもカイロギがわく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,彼女の所へ行ってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,薬　飲んどいた方が身のためだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:48.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,では　私も嬢ちゃんと話すのやめた方がいいと？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:50.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,嬢ちゃんは薬を飲むと？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　どうだかね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっと無理ね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:08.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子　ひどく寂しがり屋で　臆病で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私にも薬をいただけませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:23.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これを機に　もう繋がりを絶ちたいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミが薬を…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あと　これを預かってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:50.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな　どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつでも困ったら呼んでねって言ったじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:04.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当は　ずっと　迷惑だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　そうなの　スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:15.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だったら　謝るから　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,答えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,泣いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの　何があったの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,答えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう薬を飲んでしまったの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゆら　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何やってんだ　いい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かったわ　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,薬　飲むから一人にして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミが泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:52.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの　何があったの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:59.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私も少しは役に立てるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:05.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと頼ってばかりで　ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミ　話がある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:28.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,里へ帰すと？私何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:34.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　お前は母親代わりに本当によくやってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だがゆらはお前が来てから弱くなる一方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:46.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前に懐く余り　他のものを拒むようになってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,外で遊ぶこともせず
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前とは話さなくても心が通じるなどと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それを諭せばますます拒む
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:06.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前がそばにおる限り　ゆらは変わらんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:12.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまないが　あの子のためなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:25.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうよ　これでいいのよ　これで…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:58.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だめ　もうスミに頼っちゃ　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:03.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だめ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここ　どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,町にあったかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:11.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰も…いない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙なものが泳いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだ　戻らなきゃ　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,戻ってスミの所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,竿がない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,違う　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっちへ行きたいんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:55.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どの枝も届きそうで届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どんどん流されてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:23.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,怖い　そっちは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰か　お願い助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:50.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何　どうしたの　あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:56.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか今　夢に女の子が出てきて　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海に流れされそうになってて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,女の子が助けてって言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:08.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おーい　ゆら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,手分けした方がいい　俺は向こうの水路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:16.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゆら…か？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:49.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん　あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゆら　大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よかった　気がついたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:40.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと薬飲むまで見てるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ようやく懲りたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう戻れないかと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何度もああして　皆に迷惑をかけられないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:05.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだ　スミ　薬飲んだんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうして分かったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:13.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,結局　薬全部は飲めなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱり嬢ちゃんが心配で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:21.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だめね　わざわざあんな文まで書いたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっか　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:29.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　やっぱり寂しくなるな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:31.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:39.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,会いに行きゃいいだろう　水路は変わらず繋がってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:44.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分で漕ぐのは無理なうちは　誰かの船に乗っけてもらえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:50.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,苦しくなりゃ　町の誰かが助けてくれるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ね　父さん　私そうしていい？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:06.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミ　私会いに行っていい？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もちろんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミ　遊びに来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スミ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:00.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また合図を送ったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:04.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいでしょう　たまーになんだから
